OL,3,CCooper: British couple's 10-year
OL,4,Csentence in Iran 'totally
OL,5,Cunjustifiable'
OL,7,FThe Foreign Secretary has labelled a
OL,8,F10-year jail sentence for a British
OL,9,Fcouple in Iran as "totally
OL,10,Funjustifiable".
OL,12,FLindsay and Craig Foreman were
OL,13,Farrested in January 2025 while
OL,14,Ftravelling through the country on an
OL,15,Faround-the-world motorcycle journey
OL,16,Fand detained on charges of espionage.
OL,18,FThe couple, from East Sussex who are
OL,19,Fbeing held in Tehran's Evin prison,
OL,20,Fdeny the allegations.
