OL,3,CCooper: British couple's 10-year
OL,4,Csentence in Iran 'totally
OL,5,Cunjustifiable'
OL,7,F"This sentence is completely appalling
OL,8,Fand totally unjustifiable," said
OL,9,FYvette Cooper.
OL,11,F"We will pursue this case relentlessly
OL,12,Fwith the Iranian government until we
OL,13,Fsee Craig and Lindsay Foreman safely
OL,14,Freturned to the UK and reunited with
OL,15,Ftheir family.
OL,17,F"In the meantime, their welfare is our
OL,18,Fpriority and we will continue to
OL,19,Fprovide consular assistance to them
OL,20,Fand their families."
