OL,3,CCooper: British couple's 10-year
OL,4,Csentence in Iran 'totally
OL,5,Cunjustifiable'
OL,7,FJoe Bennett, Lindsay Foreman's son,
OL,8,Ftold ITV News they had been informed
OL,9,Fof the sentence last week and his
OL,10,Ffamily was "deeply concerned" for the
OL,11,Fpair's welfare and the "lack of
OL,12,Ftransparency" in their judicial
OL,13,Fprocess.
OL,15,F"My parents have now been sentenced to
OL,16,F10 years following a trial that lasted
OL,17,Fjust three hours and in which they
OL,18,Fwere not allowed to present a
OL,19,Fdefence," he said.
