OL,5,Cunjustifiable'
OL,7,F"They have consistently denied the
OL,8,Fallegations. We have seen no evidence
OL,9,Fto support the charge of espionage."
OL,11,FHe added: "We were previously told
OL,12,Fthat once sentencing occurred, further
OL,13,Faction would follow. We now hope the
OL,14,FUK Government will act decisively and
OL,15,Fuse every available avenue to secure
OL,16,Ftheir release."
