OL,5,Cunjustifiable'
OL,7,FIn January, Mr Bennett was joined by
OL,8,Fformer detainee Anoosheh Ashoori and
OL,9,FRichard Ratcliffe, who fought a public
OL,10,Fcampaign that involved two hunger
OL,11,Fstrikes to have his wife Nazanin
OL,12,FZaghari-Ratcliffe freed from Iran, at
OL,13,Fthe steps of Number 10 Downing Street
OL,14,Fto deliver a 70,000-signature petition
OL,15,Fcalling on the Government to do more
OL,16,Fto free them.
OL,18,FAhead of his sentencing, Mr Foreman
OL,19,Fsaid he had a one-word message for the
OL,20,FUK Government.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
