OL,3,CCooper: British couple's 10-year
OL,4,Csentence in Iran 'totally
OL,5,Cunjustifiable'
OL,7,F"One word would be: help. Full stop,"
OL,8,Fhe told ITV News.
OL,10,F"I don't understand why we have been
OL,11,Fhere for 13 months, being held hostage
OL,12,Fin 2026. In what day and age does this
OL,13,F(happen)? When does this end?"
OL,15,FHe described being held in an "eight-
OL,16,Ffoot cell with a hole in the floor and
OL,17,Fa sink" and described the effects of
OL,18,F57 days in solitary confinement,
OL,19,Fsaying: "Emotionally and physically,
OL,20,Fit broke me to pieces".
