OL,7,FThe couple is due to appear before a
OL,8,Fcourt in Tehran in the coming days.
OL,10,FCraig Foreman said the infrequent
OL,11,Fmeetings with his wife are what
OL,12,Fsustain him.
OL,14,F"I know her prison is just 70 metres
OL,15,Faway, and I get to see her once a
OL,16,Fmonth," he said.
OL,18,F"For me and for Lindsay, seeing each
OL,19,Fother is the only thing that's keeping
OL,20,Fus going right now. I love my wife
OL,21,Fdearly. She's the love of my life."
